@startuml seq-compose-from-contact
' Context: contacts
' SDD: PROM-PERSONAL-CONTACTS-006
' Revision: 2026-07-19

title Contacts — scorciatoia «Scrivi» da rubrica

actor Utente
participant "UI" as UI
participant "ContactsMachine" as CM
participant "NavigationMachine" as Nav

Utente -> UI : tap scrivi su contatto

alt contatto internal
  UI -> CM : ComposeFromContact(contact)
  CM --> UI : ComposePeerResolved\n(ChatPeer)
  UI -> Nav : OpenFromCompose(peer)
else contatto esterno
  UI -> CM : ComposeFromContact(contact)
  CM --> UI : ComposeRejected
  UI -> Utente : messaggio errore
end

@enduml
